data.description: Do you want to come home from work to relax? Look no further! This beautiful home has a relaxing feel, from the pond down the street; for walking, basketball, duck feed, perch fishing, playground fun or simply sitting and taking in nature or relaxing in your own back yard in the comfort of your covered patio . Your new home boasts of large living areas. It is a must see, Home has had a full interior paint job done. Primary bedroom is separate from secondary bedrooms for a more private feel but close enough to kitchen to get a midnight snack! There is even an additional living area that you can use for all kinds of entertainment, from a TV room, game room, play room to a place of solace for crafts, small indoor shop, or an office away from all.  Come see your new home to see how this fits your wants and needs.
